      Driver code:
    
       - Add the sched_clock for the arc timer (Alexey Brodkin)
    
       - Change the file timer names for riscv, rockchip, tegra20, sun4i and
         meson6 (Daniel Lezcano)
    
       - Add the DT bindings for r8a7796, r8a77470 and r8a774a1 (Biju Das)
    
